! Filter expression building blocks

These are shown inside filtered transclusions so the filter syntax is highlighted.

!! Operands

* Operator with operand: {{{ [tag[done]] }}}
* Literal title: {{{ [[Literal Title]] }}}
* Bare word title: {{{ [title[HelloThere]] }}}
* Field operator: {{{ [field:caption[My Caption]] }}}
* Variable operand: {{{ [tag<currentTiddler>] }}}
* Text reference operand: {{{ [get{!!field}] }}}
* Regexp operand: {{{ [regexp[^foo.*$]] }}}
* Multi-valued variable operand: {{{ [(myMultiValuedVariable)] }}}
* Standalone variable run: {{{ [<currentTiddler>] }}}
* Standalone transclusion run: {{{ [{!!title}] }}}
* Standalone title run: {{{ [[Some Tiddler]] }}}

!! Suffixes

* Single suffix: {{{ [search:title[term]] }}}
* Multiple suffix parts: {{{ [search:title,caption[term]] }}}
* Named suffix flags: {{{ [search:title:casesensitive,literal[Foo]] }}}

!! Negation and multiple operands

* Negated operator: {{{ [tag[done]!is[draft]] }}}
* Multiple operands: {{{ [list[a],[b],<c>] }}}
* Empty operand: {{{ [all[]] }}}

!! Run prefixes

* And (default): {{{ [tag[a]] +[sort[title]] }}}
* Optional (or): {{{ [tag[a]] ~[all[shadows]] }}}
* Negation run: {{{ [tag[a]] -[tag[b]] }}}
* Append literal run: {{{ [tag[a]] =[[ExtraTitle]] }}}
* Named `:and`: {{{ [tag[a]] :and[!is[system]] }}}
* Named `:or`: {{{ [tag[a]] :or[tag[b]] }}}
* Named `:filter`: {{{ [tag[a]] :filter[get[priority]match[high]] }}}
* Named `:map`: {{{ [tag[a]] :map[get[title]] }}}
* Named `:reduce`: {{{ [tag[a]] :reduce[add<accumulator>] }}}
* Named `:sort`: {{{ [tag[a]] :sort[get[modified]] }}}
* Named with suffix: {{{ [tag[a]] :reduce:flat[add<accumulator>] }}}

!! Assignment shortcut (=> / :let)

* Assign to a named variable: {{{ [tag[a]] =>savedTitles [<savedTitles>count[]] }}}
* Assign to a quoted name: {{{ [tag[a]] =>"my titles" }}}

!! Variables and MVV inside filters

* Variable and MVV together: {{{ [tag<currentTiddler>] [(mvv)] }}}
* MVV in an operand position: {{{ [enlist<myListVariable>] }}}

!! Filters in widget attributes

<$list filter="[tag[done]sort[title]limit[10]]">
* <<currentTiddler>>
</$list>

(A filter can also back a `\function` — see the //Pragmas// demo.)
